lead_paragraph: Senator Bob Corker, Republican of Tennessee, lifted his blockade of a House-Senate deal that would cut $5 trillion in spending over the next decade to balance the federal budget.

headline.print_headline: Lawmaker Ends Blockade of Budget Deal
